Alright, go ahead.

15:19.485 --> 15:22.455
Jennifer, ask
the first question.

15:22.488 --> 15:23.489
[clearing throat]

15:29.195 --> 15:31.097
‐Mr. Bartokomous...
‐Uh‐huh?

15:33.700 --> 15:35.969
