on the financing

15:36.002 --> 15:37.337
of student loans?

15:39.673 --> 15:41.174
Student loans?

15:43.309 --> 15:45.278
Boy, I wish I had a hat.

15:45.311 --> 15:46.580
‐Balki!
‐Okay, okay, okay.

15:46.613 --> 15:48.281
‐Okay, okay.
